Package: ants
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Linear Regression, Diagnostics, and Assumption Testing
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Alfarizi", "Nasaruddin",
           email = "alfaridzinasaruddin@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    Provides an integrated function 'flm' that fits linear regression models
    and returns regression equation, partial and simultaneous test results 
    (with conclusions), VIF, classical assumptions diagnostics (normality, 
    heteroskedasticity, autocorrelation) and interpretation of R-squared values.
